source.name: DOF: Summary of Neighborhood Sales for Manhattan for Class 1-, 2- and 3-Family homes - 2009
source.description: The Department of Finance (DOF) maintains records for all property sales in New York City, including sales of family homes in each borough. This list is a summary of neighborhood sales for Class 1-, 2- and 3-Family homes in Manhattan in 2009.
